snippet: Carl Edwards pulled away on a late start to snap a 70-race winless streak, the second long drought he has ended at Phoenix International Raceway.
abstract: Carl Edwards wins at Phoenix International Raceway, his first Nascar Sprint Cup victory since 2011.
lead_paragraph: Carl Edwards pulled away on a late start to snap a 70-race winless streak, the second long drought he has ended at Phoenix International Raceway.
